Alpha (Α).title: The Trailblazer 🚀
Alpha (Α).personality: Confident, ambitious, and natural-born leaders. Alphas take charge, thrive in competition, and inspire others with their determination.

Sigma (Σ).title: The Lone Strategist 🎭
Sigma (Σ).personality: Independent and mysterious, Sigmas walk their own path. They’re highly intelligent and prefer working alone rather than leading a crowd.

Tau (Τ).title: The Fearless Warrior ⚔️
Tau (Τ).personality: Brave, direct, and action-driven. Taus never back down from a challenge and are always pushing forward, no matter the obstacles.

Omega (Ω).title: The Resilient Rebel 🔥
Omega (Ω).personality: Unconventional and strong-willed, Omegas don’t follow the crowd. They embrace their uniqueness and thrive in adversity.

Beta (Β).title: The Scholar 📚
Beta (Β).personality: Logical, analytical, and curious. Betas love learning, problem-solving, and diving deep into intellectual challenges.

Delta (Δ).title: The Thinker 🤔
Delta (Δ).personality: Deep and introspective, Deltas question everything and seek meaning in the world. They are great at seeing patterns others miss.

Psi (Ψ).title: The Visionary 🌌
Psi (Ψ).personality: Creative, philosophical, and ahead of their time. Psis think beyond the present and explore ideas that others might not understand yet.

Pi (Π).title: The Perfectionist 🎯
Pi (Π).personality: Detail-oriented and precise, Pis are methodical and hardworking. They excel in structured environments and have a strong work ethic.

Gamma (Γ).title: The Life of the Party 🎉
Gamma (Γ).personality: Energetic, fun-loving, and full of charisma. Gammas light up any room and bring people together effortlessly.

Lambda (Λ).title: The Artist 🎨
Lambda (Λ).personality: Expressive, creative, and deeply emotional. Lambdas channel their feelings into their art, music, or storytelling.

Omicron (Ο).title: The Diplomat 🤝
Omicron (Ο).personality: Balanced and fair-minded, Omicrons are great mediators who bring people together and solve conflicts with ease.

Rho (Ρ).title: The Empath ❤️
Rho (Ρ).personality: Compassionate and understanding, Rhos deeply connect with others and often take on the emotions of those around them.

Epsilon (Ε).title: The Reliable One 🏡
Epsilon (Ε).personality: Loyal, dependable, and always there when you need them. Epsilons are the backbone of any group, making sure things get done.

Zeta (Ζ).title: The Practical Genius 🛠️
Zeta (Ζ).personality: Resourceful and pragmatic, Zetas focus on real-world solutions and know how to turn ideas into reality.

Kappa (Κ).title: The Hard Worker 💪
Kappa (Κ).personality: Disciplined and patient, Kappas believe in persistence. They don’t rush, but they always reach their goals.

Mu (Μ).title: The Silent Force 🌿
Mu (Μ).personality: Quiet but powerful, Mus don’t seek attention but their presence is deeply felt. They work behind the scenes and make things happen.

Nu (Ν).title: The Deep Thinker 🌊
Nu (Ν).personality: Thoughtful and introspective, Nus often reflect on life’s big questions and have a calm, wise aura.

Iota (Ι).title: The Minimalist 🎐
Iota (Ι).personality: Simple, efficient, and focused. Iotas don’t waste time on unnecessary things—they value what truly matters.

Theta (Θ).title: The Rebel Genius 🌀
Theta (Θ).personality: Unpredictable and highly creative, Thetas think outside the box and challenge the status quo.

Eta (Η).title: The Free Spirit 🌬️
Eta (Η).personality: Spontaneous and adventurous, Etas follow their heart and seek new experiences without fear of the unknown.

Xi (Ξ).title: The Trickster 🃏
Xi (Ξ).personality: Witty, mischievous, and always one step ahead. Xis love surprises, puzzles, and playing with ideas.

Chi (Χ).title: The Chaos Bringer 🌪️
Chi (Χ).personality: Energetic and unconventional, Chis thrive in unpredictability and love shaking things up just to see what happens.

Phi (Φ).title: The Dreamer ☁️
Phi (Φ).personality: Idealistic and full of imagination, Phis see beauty in the world that others often overlook.

Upsilon (Υ).title: The Wildcard 🎲
Upsilon (Υ).personality: Impossible to categorize, Upsilons are a mix of everything. They follow their own logic and embrace life's randomness.
